                <head>120. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d120fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files
                        (H–Files), Box 107. Secret. The meeting took place in the White House
                        Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
